'''阿尔弗雷德·乔凡尼·隆卡里·鲍伊'''，[[英帝國官佐勳章|OBE]]（{{lang-en|'''Alfred Giovanni Roncalli Boe'''}} {{post-nominals|country=GBR|OBE}} ，{{bd|1973年|9月29日|||Boe, Alfie}}）是一名英国男高音歌唱家和演员,尤其活跃在音乐剧表演领域。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.decca.com/artists/alfie-boe-15569|title=Decca Records - Alfie Boe |accessdate=2011-07-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110430114957/http://www.decca.com/artists/alfie-boe-15569|archivedate=2011-04-30|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

2010年10月，《[[悲惨世界|悲惨世界]]》：25周年音乐会在伦敦女王剧院举办，他在《[[悲慘世界_(音樂劇)|悲惨世界]]》[[音樂劇|音乐剧]]表演中扮演尚萬強，后又在[[百老匯|百老汇]]再次表演。他的表演在国际上广受好评，并因此闻名世界。在百老汇2016年3月29日开始的《[[尋找新樂園|寻找梦幻岛]]》剧中，他一直担任主角。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.broadway.com/buzz/183889/alfie-boe-will-replace-tony-yazbeck-in-finding-neverland-sally-ann-triplett-steps-in-for-sandy-duncan/|title=Alfie Boe Will Replace Tony Yazbeck in Finding Neverland; Sally Ann Triplett Steps In for Sandy Duncan|website=Broadway.com|access-date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031074528/https://www.broadway.com/buzz/183889/alfie-boe-will-replace-tony-yazbeck-in-finding-neverland-sally-ann-triplett-steps-in-for-sandy-duncan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
而且，鲍伊因为2002年[[巴茲·雷曼|巴茨·鲁尔曼]]执导复演的《[[波希米亚人_(歌剧)|波西米亚人]]》而和表演团队成员共同荣获2003年的托尼奖。<ref name="hollywood">{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/les-miserables-alfie-boe-broadway-371560|title=Tony Winner Alfie Boe Could Revive 'Les Miserables' Role on Broadway|last=Carlson|first=Erin|date=2012-09-19|publisher=''[[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]]''|accessdate=2014-06-11|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126003606/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/les-miserables-alfie-boe-broadway-371560|dead-url=no}}</ref>
在英国，他已经卖出了一百多万张专辑。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/what-to-listen-to/alfie-boe-and-michael-ball-join-forces-for-album-and-premiere-vi/|title=Alfie Boe and Michael Ball join forces for album and premiere video for Together|publisher=|access-date=2017-02-28|archive-date=2018-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180923162607/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/what-to-listen-to/alfie-boe-and-michael-ball-join-forces-for-album-and-premiere-vi/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 背景 ==
鲍伊出生在[[蘭開夏|兰开夏郡]]的[[黑潭|布莱克浦]]，在[[弗利特伍德|弗利特伍德]]长大，他是家中九个孩子里最小的。<ref name="Gazette2124792">{{Cite news|url=http://www.blackpoolgazette.co.uk/entertainment-news/Royal-honour-for-Fleetwood-opera.2124792.jp|title=Royal honour for Fleetwood opera star|date=2007-03-15|publisher={{tsl|en|Blackpool Gazette||Blackpool Gazette}}|accessdate=2008-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713102240/https://www.blackpoolgazette.co.uk/whats-on/royal-honour-for-fleetwood-opera-star-1-411531|archive-date=2019-07-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>他拥有爱尔兰和挪威血统。他的母亲和父亲给他起的意大利名字叫波普·约翰二十三世。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/theobserver/2010/may/30/alfie-boe-eno-pearl-fishers|title=Alfie Boe: 'The Pearl Fishers is what opera should be about' | Interview | From the Observer | The Observer|last=Kate Kellaway|date=2010-05-30|publisher=Guardian|accessdate=2013-08-06|location=London|archive-date=2018-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710010703/https://www.theguardian.com/theobserver/2010/may/30/alfie-boe-eno-pearl-fishers|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-2277559/Alfie-Boe-Former-car-mechanic-turned-tenor-39-noisy-childhood-tricky-departure-opera.html|title=Alfie Boe: Former car mechanic turned tenor, 39, on his noisy childhood and tricky departure from opera | Mail Online|last=Joanna Moorhead|date=2013-02-17|publisher=Dailymail.co.uk|accessdate=2013-08-06|location=London|archive-date=2016-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160225183017/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-2277559/Alfie-Boe-Former-car-mechanic-turned-tenor-39-noisy-childhood-tricky-departure-opera.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他先后在圣沃尔斯坦和圣埃德蒙学校和艾伦主教天主教高中学习。

他最早的音乐记忆来自于他父亲的[[理查德·贝尔克雷迪伯爵|理查德·陶贝尔]]的录音带。在他11岁时，他第一次看到了[[贾科莫·普契尼|普契尼]]的歌剧《波希米亚人》。<ref name="Gazette3729439">{{Cite news|url=http://www.blackpoolgazette.co.uk/blackpoolnews/Fyldeborn-star-gets-hero39s-welcome.3729439.jp|title=Fylde-born star gets hero's welcome|last=Ettridge|first=Lisa|date=2008-01-31|publisher={{tsl|en|Blackpool Gazette||Blackpool Gazette}}|accessdate=2008-03-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080201040734/http://www.blackpoolgazette.co.uk/blackpoolnews/Fyldeborn-star-gets-hero39s-welcome.3729439.jp|archivedate=2008-02-01}}</ref>{{Fact|date=March 2008}}{{Fact|date=March 2008}}

14岁时，鲍伊在福利特伍德霍尔的音乐老师罗蒂道森举办的“演出之音”演唱会上首次进行公开表演。后来他说，虽然他的演唱只有几行，但是当时非常紧张。

17岁时,鲍伊成为布莱克浦比斯法姆的TVR工厂的学徒技师。<ref name="Gazette1885161">{{Cite news|url=http://www.blackpoolgazette.co.uk/blackpoolnews/Superstar-hope-for-Fleetwood-tenor.1885161.jp|title=Superstar hope for Fleetwood tenor|date=2006-11-18|publisher={{tsl|en|Blackpool Gazette||Blackpool Gazette}}|accessdate=2008-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713102240/https://www.blackpoolgazette.co.uk/news/superstar-hope-for-fleetwood-tenor-1-403972|archive-date=2019-07-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
在他平常擦汽车的时候，他和同事一起唱着歌剧的咏叹调享受生活的乐趣。一天，一个从事音乐行業相关的客户无意中听到，並對他留下深刻的印象，客户建议他应该到伦敦的奥义李歌剧公司面试。他的面试成功了，随后放弃了抛光汽车，转而从事歌唱事业。如果当时鲍伊没有能够听从客户的建议去试镜,就会失去这次成功的机会。<ref name="ClassicFM20080921">{{Cite episode|airdate=2008-09-21|series=The DNA-List with Danny Wallace|title=The DNA-List: Alfie Boe|url=http://www.classicfm.co.uk/Article.asp?id=871345&spid=27924|network={{tsl|en|Classic FM (UK)||Classic FM}}|access-date=2017-02-28|archive-date=2019-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713102242/https://www.classicfm.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

